# Customer Segmentation Project

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes customer data to group customers based on behavior.

## 📊 Tools Used
- Excel
- Python (Pandas)
- Jupyter Notebook

## 📁 Dataset
The dataset contains customer age, income, and spending score.

## 🔍 Key Insights
- High income customers tend to spend more
- Some low income customers still have high spending behavior

